  <name>Ghostty</name>
  <summary>Fast, feature-rich, and cross-platform terminal emulator</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Ghostty is a terminal emulator that differentiates itself by being
      fast, feature-rich, and native. While there are many excellent
      terminal emulators available, they all make tradeoffs between speed,
      features, and native platform integration. Ghostty attempts to push
      the boundaries on all three.
    </p>
  </description>
